content: Hi Sue! Thanks for reaching out! You can look in the announcements channel to see when texting will happen, then look at texting campaigns to click on the links for the actual texting. Thanks for being here!
I have done both, and 11:30 am ET has come and gone.  There have been no further links in texting campaigns.
Sometimes they post campaigns randomly, so please keep an eye on the channel. Thanks so much for being here!
